  "prompt": "In some countries, young people are encouraged to work or travel for a year between finishing high school and starting university. Discuss the advantages and disadvantages.",
  "prompt_jp": "ギャップイヤーの欠点と自分の意見を述べよ。",
  "outline_jp": [
    "利点: 実社会で学び大人の生活を味わう",
    "例: 時間を守るなど実践的スキル",
    "譲歩: ホームシックになりやすい",
    "欠点: 勉強の習慣に戻りにくい",
    "結論: 有益だが親と相談を"
  ],
  "model_answer": [
    "One advantage of a gap year is that you learn in the real world, getting a taste of adult life.",
    "For instance, work teaches punctuality, such as arriving on time every day.",
    "Admittedly, there are disadvantages: many people get homesick after a few weeks abroad.",
    "There is also a risk that people forget how to study and find it hard to get back into the habit of doing homework.",
    "In conclusion, although a gap year builds useful life skills, young people should discuss setting off with their parents."
  ],
